    <h3 class="rail-article-title">
      <a class="article-permalink" href="http://time.com/3583635/dumb-and-dumber-to-movie-review/" data-event="tile">Review: Can&#8217;t Get Much Dummer Than <i>Dumb and Dumber To</i></a>
        
