    <a class="time-icons time-icons-linkedin social-link-linkedin popup" href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3596961%2Freview-the-imitation-game%2F&title=Review%3A+The+Imitation+Game%3A+Dancing+With+Dr.+Strange" data-event="linkedin" title="Click to post this article to LinkedIn"></a>
