    	     <a class="time-icons time-icons-tw social-link-tw popup" href="#" data-href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5HMd-f28f&text=Channing%20Tatum%27s%20role%20in%20%22Foxcatcher%22%20is%20most%20daring&via=TIMECulture" data-event="tweet-lwr" title="Click to Tweet this article"></a>
    	     <a class="time-icons time-icons-mail social-link social-link-mail" href="mailto:?subject=Review%3A%20Foxcatcher%E2%80%99s%20Mat%20Madness%20%7C%20TIME&body=Review%3A%20Foxcatcher%E2%80%99s%20Mat%20Madness%0A%0ATatum%20scores%20a%20reversal%0D%0A%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3583119%2Freview-foxcatchers-mat-madness%2F" data-event="email-lwr" title="Click to Email this article"></a>
