    <h2 class="article-title" itemprop="headline">REVIEW: <i>The Theory of Everything</i>: My Left Brain</h2>
  <div class="article-sub-headline">
    <div class="article-meta">

        <ul class="article-authors">
            <li class="article-author ">
              <span class="byline"><a itemprop="author" href="http://time.com/author/richard-corliss/">Richard Corliss</a></span>
              
